You must have recently edited your client.java but it has an error so it can’t compile. Try undoing something you recently did in your client.java. I’ve been coding for 1 week now. Don’t take my advice seriously. I’m only trying to help the best way i can.
If that doesn’t work then:
You should try downloading “eclipse”, search on Google. Try opening your .java with that. It will spot the error and will tell you on which line it’s on.

EDIT: EconomyReset.java might be the problem too.
